'''大西洋沿岸平原'''（{{lang-en|Atlantic coastal plain}}）是[[美國東岸|美國東岸]][[大西洋|大西洋]]沿岸的一片[[平原|平原]]。它从{{link-en|纽约湾|New York Bight}}向南延伸2200英里(3500公里)，直至[[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]]與[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]交界地帶。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Atlantic Coastal Plain|url=http://www.geo.hunter.cuny.edu/bight/coastal.html|author=Stoffer|first=Phil|work=Geology and Geography of New York Bight Beaches|access-date=2020-08-10|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202162741/http://www.geo.hunter.cuny.edu/bight/coastal.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=South Atlantic Coastal Plain|url=http://www.blm.gov/wildlife/pl_03sum.htm|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090424093048/http://www.blm.gov/wildlife/pl_03sum.htm|archivedate=2009-04-24|access-date=2020-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>平原的範圍大致為大西洋海岸向内陆延伸约50至100公里。

大西洋沿岸平原的平均海拔高度不超过900米，平原內有许多河流、[[草沼|草沼]]和[[树沼|树沼]] <ref>{{Cite web|title=Atlantic Coastal Plain Lesson for Kids - Study.com|url=http://www.study.com/academy/lesson/atlantic-coastal-plain-lesson-for-kids.html|publisher=|access-date=2020-08-10|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728185102/https://study.com/academy/lesson/atlantic-coastal-plain-lesson-for-kids.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

